,"tid":50032,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T17:00:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家幾耐跑一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n隔晚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3977a59c7c225413d0d65b44eda98a108d4174e","tid":50032,"uid":64463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T17:14:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大家幾耐跑一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n隔晚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n隔晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3f1a92a709baaedfa36ec9495238eedf5d57af8","tid":50032,"uid":2114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T17:26:39.000Z","msg":"一般跑10km<br />\n<br />\n鞋就asics <br />\n衫就淘寶啲透氣衫<br />\n褲都係淘寶運動短褲<br />\n<br />\n早排會腰包+手機+八達通+紙巾+鎖鑰<br />\n呢排就紙巾+鎖鑰就算"},{"pid":"f14868bb3bfcee3571a5301d2df70ddaafc1e150","tid":50032,"uid":24900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T17:36:43.000Z","msg":"帶腰包會跑得唔舒服     跑半馬帶野真係想死 <br />\n所以粉嶺跑去吐露港或者大圍跑去吐露港係唔錯<br />\n中間有間百佳   又有海風"},{"pid":"c13b7a072f5e72cdb061c6e9d89ac837553a1a4a","tid":50032,"uid":18977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T17:37:51.000Z","msg":"跑開4-5k 因爲兩邊一邊就墳場一邊就隧道冇位跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上身著件Nike pro combat 跑耐咗就夠暖 <br />\n下身Nike dri fit 露脾 跑嗰陣唔會卡住 有時凍就搭條legging但好撚唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鞋就free run 5.0 個底唔硬又易屈 <br />\n水就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 翻屋企先飲"},{"pid":"80368e8c29c02a4fb193bd4259b8b3646b1fc696","tid":50032,"uid":40445,"like":0