b02c019b3048895c1","tid":50032,"uid":17722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:37:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大家幾耐跑一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n隔晚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n隔晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係隔晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黎緊天氣凍, 大家點著?<br />\n本身我著開Nike pro全身打底"},{"pid":"9ee4a608faa276b8159b03b254ed3f57f178e5c3","tid":50032,"uid":15757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:42:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>必備$100 + 八達通<br />\n10K：衣著隨意得啦睇天氣啦，裝備無，留意下附近啲水站唔駛水樽<br />\n半馬：衣著隨意得啦睇天氣啦（肥仔可以著tight褲唔會磨脾），電話加耳機，放到電話同水樽的腰包</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大人"},{"pid":"1863c9113afaf6830f1b3becf22f1b461c70b687","tid":50032,"uid":17873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:42:41.000Z","msg":"大家咁考究係為咗提升表現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：求其著+mizuno"},{"pid":"d4ea07dd6fb94ae3686c12cae7842e4f2b4e19ab","tid":50032,"uid":17722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:45:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>跑個步都咁多野搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n算少，大把人電話，耳機，跑步錶，水樽.....但跑2K就話頂唔順</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nArmband必備唔少得，唔通用手攞咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n耳機就有便有貴，藍芽無線就舒服d既<br />\n自己就用普通有線<br />\n錶就唔似人地咁pro用Garmin<br />\nFitbit有heart rate已經夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed1bd42a2c46312add694a98c864dceb51fcd29c","tid":50032,"uid":12889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:47:52.000Z","msg":"啱啱開始跑左兩三次，平時冇乜點跑開<br />\naround 7K跑左45分鐘左右<br />\n應該點練先可以1個鐘內跑完10k?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38234d5660c0adc45937a47098bb978ee97ae2d7","tid":50032,"uid":49707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:48:03.000Z","msg":"我又係一定要帶tissue. 果D 來。估唔到有人同我一樣"},{"pid":"d8da817a3fa485b08ef1f30e4407308a875da347","tid":50032,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:49:58.000Z","msg":"粗著既跑鞋 跑褲 普通t-shirt<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8410fa3b510ef5db47b7983b0e97a738e9673ee","tid":50032,"uid":9436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:59:10.000Z","msg":"隔日跑 一開始四百米都跑到想死<br />\n而家最多一口氣均速八公里<br />\n不過磅數重都跑得唔快亦唔敢跑太多<br />\n每次都係45分鐘至一個鐘內<br />\n同真正跑手仲有好大段距離 但同自己比係進步咗好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n舊TEE+跑褲+ADIDAS跑鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n臂帶袋電話+藍牙耳筒<br />\n屋企樓下運動場跑所以乜鳩都唔帶"},{"pid":"71e2f0d522c70553a3e81fb4f1f9122f57ccf83d","tid":50032,"uid":10949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T14:18:56.000Z","msg":"衫：背心或短袖衫<br />\n褲：壓力褲<br />\n裝備：garmin錶,運動腰包,八達通,$100,plantronics藍芽,毛巾<br />\n<br />\n鎖匙放信箱淨係袋信箱匙<br />\n花士令搽lin,爽身粉拍蘿柚<br />\n<br />\n話時話，跑到咁上下lin頭pat花士令乾左都係磨lin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇咩其他辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d9bb9a4740796000111c2f1bbf73d1cf0df9040","tid":50032,"uid":3381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T14:21:46.000Z","msg":"近排風褸加tight 入面求其<br />\n加隻garmin 有時帶埋電話同藍芽耳機聽歌<br />\n鞋就wave rider 18"},{"pid":"b16a950279c3ae2fe55f707c36ed0cf96aac522b","tid":50032,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-11T13:56:02.000Z","msg":"短褲，衫 唔帶電話，剩係身份證同水樽揸手"},{"pid":"72cbc5831db1df4a0738ccc68f56bfd2268993de","tid":50032,"uid":71369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-12T14:46:08.